name: merfishtools

owner.description: Bioconda is a distribution of bioinformatics software realized as a channel for the versatile Conda package manager.
owner.name: bioconda

summary: MERFISHtools implement a Bayesian framework for accurately predicting gene or transcript expression from MERFISH data. On top, differential expression analysis can be performed for two or multiple conditions, including credible intervals for fold change and coefficient of variation, and controlling the expected false discovery rate.
